trans-unit.source: Configures the output cache settings for application pages .
trans-unit.target: Konfigurerer du innstillinger for utdatabuffer for programsider.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: The OutputCacheSettingsSection class allows you to programmatically access and modify the `outputCacheSettings` element of the `caching` section in a configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Klassen OutputCacheSettingsSection gjør det mulig å programmatisk tilgang til og endre den `outputCacheSettings` element av den `caching` delen i en konfigurasjonsfil.

trans-unit.source: The output cache settings define the dependencies (the relationships between items stored in the cache and files, cache keys, or <xref:System.Web.Caching.CacheDependency> objects) that are used in output caching, for instance, by the [@ OutputCache](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/28a9e101-fb44-4198-9cb6-b8a52312fec2) directive or by the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.OutputCacheProfile>.
trans-unit.target: Innstillingene for utdatabuffer definerer avhengighetene (relasjoner mellom elementer som er lagret i hurtigbufferen og filer, hurtigbufferen nøkler, eller <xref:System.Web.Caching.CacheDependency>objekter) som er brukt i bufring av utdata for forekomsten av den [@ OutputCache](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/28a9e101-fb44-4198-9cb6-b8a52312fec2) direktivet eller <xref:System.Web.Configuration.OutputCacheProfile>.</xref:System.Web.Configuration.OutputCacheProfile> </xref:System.Web.Caching.CacheDependency>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The OutputCacheSettingsSection can write information into the related section of the configuration file according to the restrictions defined by the section property <xref:System.Configuration.SectionInformation.AllowDefinition%2A> whose value is <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationAllowDefinition>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > For OutputCacheSettingsSection kan skrive informasjon til delen relaterte konfigurasjonsfilen i henhold til begrensningene som er definert av den delen egenskapen <xref:System.Configuration.SectionInformation.AllowDefinition%2A>der verdien er <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationAllowDefinition>.</xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationAllowDefinition> </xref:System.Configuration.SectionInformation.AllowDefinition%2A>

trans-unit.source: Any attempt to write in a configuration file at a level not allowed in the hierarchy will result in an error message generated by the parser.
trans-unit.target: Forsøk på å skrive til konfigurasjonsfilen på et nivå ikke tillatt i hierarkiet vil føre til en feilmelding som er generert av parseren.

trans-unit.source: However, you can use this class to read configuration information at any level in the hierarchy.
trans-unit.target: Du kan imidlertid bruke denne klassen kan lese konfigurasjonsinformasjon under noen nivå i hierarkiet.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.OutputCacheSettingsSection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.OutputCacheSettingsSection"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The OutputCacheSettingsSection constructor is not intended to be used directly from your code.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktøren OutputCacheSettingsSection skal ikke brukes direkte fra koden.

trans-unit.source: It is called by the ASP.NET configuration system.
trans-unit.target: Kalles av ASP.NET Konfigurasjonssystemet.

trans-unit.source: You obtain an instance of the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.OutputCacheSettingsSection> class by using the <xref:System.Configuration.Configuration.GetSection%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Du hente en forekomst av den <xref:System.Web.Configuration.OutputCacheSettingsSection>klassen ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Configuration.Configuration.GetSection%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Configuration.Configuration.GetSection%2A> </xref:System.Web.Configuration.OutputCacheSettingsSection>

trans-unit.source: Gets a <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.OutputCacheProfileCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Gets a <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.OutputCacheProfileCollection"></xref>.

trans-unit.source: The OutputCacheProfiles property allows you to programmatically access the `outputCacheProfiles` element in a configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen OutputCacheProfiles gjør at du programmatisk tilgang av `outputCacheProfiles` element i en konfigurasjonsfil.

trans-unit.source: You can use the OutputCacheProfiles property to modify the `outputCacheProfiles` element programmatically.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke OutputCacheProfiles-egenskapen til å endre den `outputCacheProfiles` elementet programmatisk.

trans-unit.source: The `outputCacheProfiles` section contains <xref:System.Web.Configuration.OutputCacheProfile> objects that represent output cache settings that may be used by pages in the application.
trans-unit.target: Den `outputCacheProfiles` delen inneholder <xref:System.Web.Configuration.OutputCacheProfile>innstillinger som kan brukes av sider i programmet for objekter som representerer output-hurtigbuffer.</xref:System.Web.Configuration.OutputCacheProfile>

trans-unit.source: These settings can be applied to a page by setting the `CacheProfile` attribute of the [@ OutputCache](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/28a9e101-fb44-4198-9cb6-b8a52312fec2) directive.
trans-unit.target: Disse innstillingene kan brukes på en side ved å angi den `CacheProfile` for den [@ OutputCache](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/28a9e101-fb44-4198-9cb6-b8a52312fec2) direktivet.

trans-unit.source: Apply the profile to control caching attributes such as dependencies, cache location, and cache expiration time.
trans-unit.target: Bruke profilen på kontroll hurtigbufring attributter som avhengigheter, hurtigbufferplasseringen og hurtigbufferen tidspunktet for utløp.

trans-unit.source: The [@ OutputCache](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/28a9e101-fb44-4198-9cb6-b8a52312fec2) directive can override all the settings contained by an <xref:System.Web.Configuration.OutputCacheProfile> except the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.OutputCacheProfile.Enabled%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Den [@ OutputCache](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/28a9e101-fb44-4198-9cb6-b8a52312fec2) direktivet kan overstyre alle innstillingene som inneholder en <xref:System.Web.Configuration.OutputCacheProfile>bortsett fra de <xref:System.Web.Configuration.OutputCacheProfile.Enabled%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.Configuration.OutputCacheProfile.Enabled%2A> </xref:System.Web.Configuration.OutputCacheProfile>

trans-unit.source: This is to ensure you can enable or disable the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.OutputCacheProfile> without having to modify the directives in all the pages that might have overridden it.
trans-unit.target: Dette er at du kan aktivere eller deaktivere den <xref:System.Web.Configuration.OutputCacheProfile>uten å endre instruksjonene for alle sidene som har overstyrt det.</xref:System.Web.Configuration.OutputCacheProfile>

trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.OutputCacheProfileCollection"></xref> of <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.OutputCacheProfile"></xref> objects
